title: Silent Hill 4: The Room playthrough ‚Äî Part 3
description: God this game got difficult at the end. Also out of the four endings I got the worst one, and it seems like getting a better one probably wouldn't even be that hard, so I fucked up pretty bad. But, it's my first playthrough and I didn't get spoiled on how to get the good endings. I wasted a lot of items without knowing how important they'd be later on. Anyway, the game was fun and it's probably the most disturbing and bizarre game I've ever played.
